text: Sybil Fenton Newall was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 17 October 1854 and died on 24 June 1929. Newall competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Sybil NewallSybil Fenton Quenni NEWALL == References == Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain Category:1854 births Category:1929 deaths
